# Add this to your Supabase project secrets/environment variables

# Google Generative AI API Key
GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_KEY=your_google_ai_api_key_here

# To set this in Supabase:
# 1. Go to your Supabase project dashboard
# 2. Navigate to Settings > Edge Functions
# 3. Add the environment variable GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_KEY with your API key

# To get a Google AI API key:
# 1. Go to https://ai.google.dev/
# 2. Click "Get API key in Google AI Studio"
# 3. Create a new API key
# 4. Copy the key and add it to your Supabase environment variables